{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, they call us 4 o'clock every single night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German will come only at 8 o'clock in the morning to count us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But from 4 o'clock, you go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You go into the latrines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The latrines consisted of a big, big pit-- a hole-- with a plank with some holes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, only a minute for a person, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because there were so many that they want to be there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just, you know, like planks with holes, and you have to be there-- only a minute.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you stay a little bit longer, there were-- this-- the girls in charge, with a big stick.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They will plant the stick into the, you know, his excrement, and they will put in your mouth-- and if you don't come out of the toilet in time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So everybody was [GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We have to go there, outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after this thing, you have to go to the-- like, clean your face, or whatever, or drink water, because you were very thirsty.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the place where you can drink the water, it was a big, you know, open space full of pipes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now and then, there were holes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were not even taps-- holes in the pipe-- some coming-- some water coming out of this pipe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you have to go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, [INAUDIBLE] this time, you know, it was just about 20 minutes for all these hundreds of people, you know, who wanted to go there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was no-- not even a queue-- one jumping on top of the other one to go and reach the water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So many times, you know, by the time they call you, it's finished.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The time is finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You haven't even reach next to the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
